Luka
Gospel Of Luke
Kayǎ è́prè̤ yácû́ rǎmárǎdyǎ lahyǎ tè̤ dố a htwǒhtya bí pè̤klè̌ yětahe ari-akyǎ.
Èthǐ krwǒrǎkuô̌ prè́ phú kayǎ dố a myáhtye ná ané̤ dố kalúkhè̌ rò a hésodônyǎ luô̌ pé̤ ǔ ná tè̤ritè̤kyǎ nuôtahe héso dǐtû́ pé̤ pè̤ nuôtahe prè́.
Phúnuô akhu-akhyě, Thárádu Theophilo꤮, vǎ myápṳ̌ thè́gně tǎ̤te̤ htuô̌lò̌ hò́ tè̤htwǒhtya dố a khǎshyékhǎrya̤ tahehò́ akhu-akhyě, vǎ dyalya̤ hò́ vǎ thè́plò ná vǎ ki rǎ pé̤ nè̤ phú a htwǒhtya tôtó̤ htuô̌ tôtó̤ hénuôma a klyá ryá nyǎ prè́ vǎ tane̤ phúyě.
Thyáphú nè̤ ki thè́gně tǎ̤te̤ lò̌lá̤takli lò̌ tè̤ritè̤kyǎ má̤lakǒ phú nè̤ ithyónò́ htuô̌hò́ nuôtahe agněnuôrò, vǎ rǎ phúnuô prè́.
Tè̤dyéthè́gně Giovanni Baptista A Tè̤opacè̤̌lya̤ Ari-akyǎ
Bí Khwí Herodè htwǒ khwí dố Juda ké̤kǔ akhè̌nuô, bwídu dố amwi̤ ná Zekaria otôprè̤. Rò ènuô a opatố̤kuô̌ dố prè̤lǔtyǎ aplò́amṳ dố ǔ è́ lǔmwi̤ ná Abijah mú꤮ nukhè̌ nuôtômṳ akǔ, rò amě mwi̤ ná Elizabeth. È ma aklwǐalyǎ ícû̌tố̤ ná bwídu tahe.<sup>a</sup>
Èthǐ thè́nyě̤ lò̌ a ohtwǒprè̤ cò́te̤ryá lò̌ cò́ dố Cò́marya<sup>b</sup> a mèthènyě cò́ rò phú Byacè Cò́marya a tè̤thyótè̤thya ná a tè̤mekyǎngó̤ tahe héonuô èthǐ cṳ̌e me̤lốme̤bǎ lò̌plǐ cò́.
Elizabeth sǒphú akhu-akhyě èthǐ phúo kuô̌ lahyǎ ǔ to, htuô̌to èthǐ thè́nyě̤lò̌ a muố̤prè̤́ lǎhò́.
Tônyěnuô, shuốkhè̌ tuố̤hò́ dố Zekaria tǒ phyéní̤ tè̤me̤ dố a lya̤bè lǔ yě. A me̤ tè̤me̤ phú bwídu tôprè̤ dố tè̤lǔhǒdu akǔ.
Phú bwídu tahe lé̤klǒ onuô, ǔ nwóhtya hò́ è ná a tǒbè sû́û̌htya tè̤nuô̤mû́ dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ bínuô tônyě akhu-akhyě, a cuốnuô̌ dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ.
Bí a sû́û̌htya tè̤nuô̤mû́ akhè̌nuô, dố aklò̌nuô, ǔ kwǐcò́bè̌ró̤cò́bè̌è́ nyacò́.
Cò́marya tanémò́khuphú tôprè̤ oluô̌htya pé̤ dố Zekaria anyěhyǎ rò a kahtò o bí lé̤sû́û̌htya tè̤nuô̤mû́ akhǎlé̤ dố cò́htwó nuôtôkyě.
Bí Zekaria myáhtye tanémò́khuphú akhè̌nuô, a khyé rò a thè́isě.
Manárò tanémò́khuphú hé lǔ, “Zekaria꤮ thè́isě tǎmé̤! Cò́marya ní̤huô̌ hò́ nè̤ tè̤kwǐcò́bè̌ akhu-akhyě nè̤mě Elizabeth ki phúo pé̤ nè̤ phúprè̤khǔ tôprè̤ pǎ rò nè̤ tǒbè è́ amwǐ̤ ná Giovanni pǎ.
Shyé꤮ a o pacè̤̌lya̤ pǎ ma a ki me̤ thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ nè̤ pǎ rò kayǎ ki thè́krṳ̂̌plu thè́krṳ̂̌phè kuô̌lò̌ ná nè̤ pǎ.
È ma a ki htwǒ du dố Cò́marya a mèthènyě pǎ tôprè̤. Thòbǐthèhtyězǎ̤ bèbè, htyěsípré̤ bèbè a tǒbè eǒní̤ tôcô꤮ to. A ki lốbǎ ná Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè dố a muố̤hò́kǔ akhè̌ cò́ pǎ.
Rò a ki thǔ ka̤khyě è́nyacò́ Israelphú tahe dố èthǐ Byacè Cò́marya a o pǎ.
A ki hyǎ ré̤ ná Byacè pǎ, rò athè́plò ki hè̌shyoresò̌ rò a ki o ná taryěshyosò̌ phú Prè̤pro̤ Elia nuô pǎ. A ki me̤rè̤̌ ka̤khyě khyěthyá phè̌tahe ná phútahe pǎ. A ki buô̌tarí ka̤khyětǒ khyěthyá kayǎ ní̤dǎ kuô̌ǔ ngó̤ to nuôtahe dố prè̤cò́prè̤te̤ tahe a klyádè̌kǔ pǎ. Thyáphú kayǎ tahe ki otaritaryǎsû Byacè atè̤hyǎ pǎ yěnuôrò, a ki taritaryǎ one pé̤ kayǎ tômṳ dố Byacè agně pǎ.”
Zekaria sudyǎ tanémò́khuphú, “Yěnuôma amá̤ è̌, amá̤to è̌ nuô, vǎ ki thè́gně myálwó cyá̤ phútě? Vǎ rò vǎ muố̤prè̤́ lǎ hò́hò́, vǎmě rò a muố̤prè̤́ lǎhò́hò́.”
Rò tanémò́khuphú hésû lǔ, “Vǎ ma Gabrielè, vǎ kahtò dố Cò́marya a mèthènyě rò a nò̌hyǎlya̤ vǎ dố vǎ ki hyǎ héso pé̤ nè̤ ná tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila yětôcô nuôprè́.
Vǎ hyǎ héso pé̤ nè̤ rò nè̤ zṳ̂́eto akhu-akhyě, nè̤ ki pè́ tuố̤dố a htwǒhtya phú vǎ ò́lya̤kyǎ nè̤ nuôtônyě pǎ. Shyé꤮ ashuốakhè̌ bè pǎnuô, a ki lốhtyabǎhtya dû phú vǎ hénuô pǎ.”
Bínuôkhè̌ dố aklò̌nuô ǔ opò̤́ è́nyacò́ Zekaria rò a cuốnuô̌ onyě̤ nyacò́ dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ mame̤tě èthǐ tane̤ lahyǎ phúnuô.
Bí a hte tuố̤dố aklò̌ khè̌nuô a hébè cyá̤ pǎ èthǐ to rò èthǐ thè́gně ná a klyá myáhtye nyǎ tè̤myáhtyelwó tôcôcô dố tè̤lǔhǒdu akǔ nuô hò́. A hébè cyá̤ pǎ ná akhǎu tômû̌꤮ to rò a vû́vyá̤luô̌ prè́ ná takhukhadǎ prè́.
Rò bí a tè̤phyétè̤me̤ dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ htuô̌hò́ akhè̌nuô, Zekaria ka̤ dố ahi.
Rò a hé, “Khǒnyá̤yě Byacè me̤cwó̤ hò́ vǎ hò́. A phyékyǎ pé̤ hò́ vǎ tè̤thè́tarè̤̌ dố ǔ pacyé̤ishyé vǎ nuôtahe hò́.”
Dyéthè́gně Ná Jesǔ Ki O Pacè̤̌lya̤ Ari-akyǎ
Bí Elizabeth muố̤dò̌ bǎhò́ lè̌thuô̌thyó akhè̌nuô, Cò́marya nò̌hyǎlya̤ tanémò́khuphú Gabrielè dố vǐ̤ Nazarè dố a o dố Galilea ké̤ nuôtôvǐ̤ akǔ.
A phyéhyǎ ní̤pé̤ prè̤mòphúthè dố amwi̤ ná Maria yěnuô tôprè̤ a tè̤ritè̤kyǎ. Maria yěnuô a ò́lya̤ htuô̌hò́ dố a ki phyé ná prè̤khǔ dố amwi̤ ná Joseph yěnuô tôprè̤ hò́. Joseph ma Khwí Davi aklwǐlyǎ tǎ̤lya̤ dǐtû́ tôprè̤.
Tanémò́khuphú hyǎ dố a o rò a hé lǔ, “Cò́marya myádu khóní̤dûhò́ nè̤ hò́, rò Byacè ki okuô̌dû ná nè̤ ní꤮.”
Mò́khutanéphú hyǎ hésoluô̌ pé̤ Maria tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yěnuô, a tane̤plǒ ní̤dyé angó̤lasá to, a tane̤pyá̤tane̤sè̌ ní̤dyé nyacò́.
Tanémò́khuphú hé lǔ, “Maria꤮ thè́isě tǎmé̤ ní! Cò́marya me̤bwíme̤taryě hò́ nè̤ hò́.
Nè̤ ki muố̤dò̌htya pǎ rò nè̤ ki phúo ní̤dyé pacè̤̌ prè̤khǔphú tôprè̤ pǎ, rò è́ amwǐ̤ ná Jesǔ ní꤮.
È ma kayǎ dố abwídu-ataryěhtǔ tôprè̤ pǎ rò ǔ ki è́ è ná tè̤dutè̤htǔ tadû Cò́marya aphúkhǔ tôprè̤ pǎ. Byacè Cò́marya ki dyé htwǒ è ná khwí tôprè̤ phú aklwǐalyǎ Davi nuô pǎ.
Htuô̌rò a ki htwǒhtya Israelphú tahe akhwí pwǒ̤tôhtû̌ pwǒ̤taple pǎ rò ahtyěaké̤ nuô atadû pé̤ cyá̤ pǎ cò́ to.”
Rò Maria hésû tanémò́khuphú, “Vǎ phúthè prè́yě, vǎ ki muố̤dò̌ rò ki phúo cyá̤ phútě?”
Rò tanémò́khuphú hésû è, “Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè ki hyǎlya̤ dû dố nè̤lo̤ pǎ rò dố tè̤dutè̤htǔ tadû Cò́marya a tè̤pro̤tè̤prya̤ akhu-akhyě pǎ rò pacè̤̌phú tôprè̤ ki hyǎo pacè̤̌lya̤ pǎ. Dố tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yě akhu-akhyěrò pacè̤̌sǎsè̌ yětôprè̤nuô ǔ ki è́ lǔ ná Cò́marya aphúkhǔ pǎ.
Tane̤tuố̤dû nè̤ tôpuố̤bǔ Elizabeth nuô, a muố̤prè̤́ lǎhò́. Ǔ hé lǔ ná aphú o cyá̤ pǎto hò́ tadû́rò, khǒnyá̤yě a muố̤dò̌ bǎhò́ lè̌thuô̌thyó hò́.
Cò́marya me̤cyá̤ tè̤pwǒ̤tôcô.”
Rò Maria hésû, “Vǎ ma Byacè a lulémuố̤ tôprè̤ prè́. A ki htwǒhtyadû phú nè̤ hénuô pǎ ní꤮.” Rò tanémò́khuphú htecuố taphǎkyǎ ná lǔ.
Maria Cuốolěkuô̌ Elizabeth
Nyě̤tyato nuô, Maria otaritaryǎ ané̤ rò a htetalwǒ̤ cuố dố vǐ̤ dố a o dố solo̤ nuôtôvǐ̤, bí Judaké̤kǔ nuô.
A cuốnuô̌ dố Zekaria a hidò́kǔ rò a hémo̤héryá avyá̤ Elizabeth.
Rò bí Elizabeth ní̤huô̌ Maria hémo̤héryá lǔ akhè̌nuô, pacè̤̌phú dố ahò́kǔ yětôprè̤nuô, a kṳ́ká̤htya. Rò Elizabeth yěnuô a lốbǎhtya ná Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè.
Rò a hébèshyo, “Dố prè̤mò lò̌꤮ plǐ aklè̌nuô nè̤ ma prè̤mò dố a ní̤bè lốhò́ ǔ tè̤sò̌ri tôprè̤ hò́ rò pacè̤̌phú dố nè̤ ki phúo ní̤dyé lǔ pǎ yětôprè̤nuô a ní̤bè kuô̌dûhò́ tè̤sò̌ri hò́.
Vǎ Byacè amuố̤ cuốhyǎtuố̤ dố vǎ o me̤tě? Vǎ cuố ní̤bè khódû tè̤myádu vǎ me̤tě?
Vǎ ní̤huô̌ nè̤ hémo̤héryá vǎvǎ ná pacè̤̌phú o dố vǎhò́kǔ yětôprè̤ kṳ́ká̤htya thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ cò́.
Nè̤ zṳ̂́e ná Byacè a tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yě ki hyǎ lốhtyabǎhtya má̤lakǒ dố nè̤gně pǎ akhu-akhyě nè̤ ní̤bèhò́ tè̤sò̌ri hò́!”
Maria Irǒ Htuthè́htya Cò́marya
Maria hé,
“Vǎ ki htuthè́htya lò̌thulò̌thè́ vǎ Byacè.
Cò́marya ma prè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ vǎ tôprè̤ htuô̌to è ma vǎ Byacè tôprè̤ akhu-akhyě vǎ thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ nyacò́.
Vǎ ma a lulémuố̤ dố amèthè okuô̌ǔ to tôprè̤ manárò a thè́né̤htyabè tuố̤ vǎ. Cáhtya khǒnyá̤yě tǎ̤plehyǎnuô myěcô pwǒ̤꤮ tôcô ki è́ vǎ ná prè̤mò dố a ní̤bè tè̤sò̌ri tôprè̤ pǎ.
Me̤těhérò Cò́marya dố ashyo-asò̌ yětôprè̤ dyéo htwǒhtya pé̤hò́ vǎ tè̤acò́azǎ̤ tadû yěnuô ná a tè̤pro̤tè̤prya̤ tahe dố vǎgně hò́. Amwi̤ ma asǎsè̌.
Bí a zó̤htya atakhu dố ashyo-asò̌ yě akhè̌, kayǎ dố a tane̤du ní̤dyé ané̤ tahenuô, a ki lṳpruốlṳpryǎkyǎ lò̌ pǎ.
A dyatǎ̤kyǎ khwí shyosò̌ tahe dố èthǐ akhǎlé̤ rò a dyahtyalô̌ tapleke kayǎ dố amèthè okuô̌ǔ to nuôtahe hò́.
A dyéekò́ dyéǒbǎ hò́ kayǎ dố a ovǐ̤okò̌ tahe rò a plwǒka̤ kazuô̌kyǎ kayǎ duzá̤htyathè̌ tahe hò́.
A thè́né̤htya tuố̤bèhò́ tè̤ dố a ò́lya̤ htuô̌hò́ ná pè̤phyěpè̤phuô̌ dố꤮ nyénu nuôtahe rò a hyǎme̤cwó̤ hò́ alulé Israelphú tahe hò́.
Thyáphú a ki thè́zò̤klabèní̤ Abraham ná aklwǐalyǎ yětahe tôhtû̌ htuô̌ tôhtû̌ agněnuôrò, a thè́né̤htya ní̤dyé hò́.”
Maria cuốokuốkuô̌ ná Elizabeth yěnuô a phûbǎ cò́ thuô̌lè̌ hò́ rò a ka̤no dố ahi prè́.
Giovanni Baptista A Tè̤opacè̤̌lya̤
Bí Elizabeth ahò́athè́ tǒlè̌ hò́ akhè̌nuô, aphú oní̤ phúprè̤khǔ tôprè̤.
Kayǎ ophûowó ná lǔ bínuô tahe ná aklwǐalyǎ phûwó tahe ní̤huô̌ ná Byacè dyéluô̌ hò́ a tè̤thè́zò̤ní̤ lakǒ lǔ akhè̌nuô, èthǐ thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ kuô̌lò̌ lǔ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤.
Èthǐ lé̤klǒ o ná ki pacè̤̌ bǎhò́ agně lwǐ̤thyó hénuô, ǔ bè dû́talí ní̤pé̤ lǔphá. Bí atǒ dû́talíphá akhè̌nuô, aklwǐalyǎ tahe hyǎkuô̌ lahyǎ rò èthǐ thè́zṳ̂́ pó̤ní̤ lahyǎ amwǐ̤ ná aphè̌ Zekaria amwi̤ ní̤dû.
Manárò amuố̤ hé, “Má̤to! Tǒbè pó̤ní̤ lǔmwǐ̤ ná Giovanni.”
Èthǐ hésû amuố̤, “Dố thǐklwǐthǐlyǎ aklè̌nuô, amwi̤ ná Giovanni nuô a o tôprè̤꤮ to.”
Aphè̌ thè́zṳ̂́ è́ amwǐ̤ ná ǔpěnuô èthǐ thè́zṳ̂́ thè́gně akhu-akhyě, èthǐ dyéluô̌ lahyǎ a takhukhadǎ rò sudyǎ lǔ.
Aphè̌ kwǐ lò̤́ba rò a rǎtǎ̤, “Amwi̤ ma Giovanni.” Rò èthǐ khyéthukhyéthè́ lò̌plǐ cò́.
Bínuô tôphuốtuô̌ Zekaria hébè cyá̤ ka̤khyě rò a htuthè́htya Cò́marya.
Kayǎ ophûowó bínuô tahe khyéthukhyéthè́ lò̌plǐ cò́, rò tè̤htwǒhtya phúyěnuô a luô̌pasǐ cuốlò̌ cò́ Judaké̤ tôké̤lè̤̌ cò́.
Byacè a tè̤pro̤tè̤prya̤ yǒ okuô̌ ná pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤ akhu-akhyě, lò̌꤮ kayǎ dố a ní̤huô̌ tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yětahenuô a khyéthukhyéthè́ rò a hé lahyǎ, “Pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤nuô a ki htwǒhtya ǐtě pǎ ha?” phúnuô.
Zekaria A Tè̤hépro̤-one
Giovanni aphè̌ Zekaria lốbǎhtya ná Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè rò a hépro̤ one ré̤ Cò́marya ari-akyǎ,
“Pè̤ ki htuthè́htya ró̤lǔ Israel a Byacè Cò́marya pó꤮. Me̤těhérò a hyǎhò́ dố akayǎ tahe a o hò́ rò a hyǎ me̤lwóhteka̤ hò́ akayǎ hò́.
Dố Cò́marya a prè̤me̤tè̤phú Davi aklwǐalyǎ akǔnuô, Cò́marya dyéohtwǒhtya pé̤ hò́ pè̤ prè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ Byacè dố a o ná a taryěshyosò̌ yětôprè̤ hò́.
Cò́marya ò́lya̤ one htuô̌hò́ ná aprè̤pro̤ sǎsè̌ dố nuôkhè̌ tahe,
è ki me̤lwóhteka̤ pè̤ dố khura tahe ná kayǎ dố a thè́hte pè̤ nuôtahe a takhukǔ pǎ.
A hé ná a ki dyéluô̌ a tè̤thè́zò̤klabè dố pè̤phyěpè̤phuô̌ tahe alo̤ pǎ, htuô̌to a ki thè́né̤htya bètuố̤ khyěthyá a tè̤ò́lya̤ sǎsè̌ nuôtahe pǎ.
73-75 Pè̤ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ tôhtû̌ kayǎyě, thyáphú pè̤ ki htwǒhtya kayǎsǎsè̌, kayǎcò́kayǎte̤ dố Cò́marya anyěhyǎ nuô rò, a héklò̤héma htuô̌hò́ angó̤ ná Abraham hò́, rò a ò́lya̤nuôlya̤ htuô̌hò́ dố a ki me̤lwóhteka̤ pè̤ ná kayǎ dố a thè́hte pè̤ nuôtahe a takhukǔ rò a plwǒme̤ hò́ a tè̤me̤yě ná pè̤ hò́, rò pè̤ ki me̤ tǎ ná tè̤taròthè́ thè́isě tǎmé̤.”
Zekaria hé aphú, “Vǎphúkhǔ, ǔ ki è́ nè̤ ná tè̤dutè̤htǔ tadû Cò́marya aprè̤pro̤ tôprè̤ pǎ, me̤těhérò nè̤ ki hyǎ taritaryǎ one ré̤ pé̤ Byacè lé̤hyǎklyá agně pǎ.
Nè̤ ki héso pé̤ Byacè akayǎ è́prè̤ ná Cò́marya ki plwǒkyǎ èthǐ tè̤thû́tè̤ora pǎ, rò èthǐ ki ní̤bè tè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ pǎ.
Me̤těhérò pè̤ Cò́marya yěnuô, a thè́zò̤ní̤ nyacò́ ǔ rò a khyáthè́dǒ nyacò́. A nò̌hyǎlya̤hò́ kayǎ o dố mò́khu tôprè̤ ki hyǎ me̤lwóhteka̤ hò́ pè̤, prè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ pè̤ yětôprè̤nuô, a thyáhò́ ná tamò̤́ lǐhtyaré̤ dố mò̤́lǐbǔkhè̌ nuôhò́.
Rò tamò̤́yě a htya dố mò́lè̤̌ rò a ki lǐtakhè̌tǎ̤ pé̤ kayǎ o dố tè̤khítè̤lò̤, tè̤thyě azo̤uô akǔ nuôtahe lò̌꤮ plǐ pǎ, rò a ki zṳ̌klyázṳ̌klǒ cuố ní̤pé̤dû pè̤ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ dố tè̤kacṳ́kabè́ aklyákǔ pǎ.”
Jesǔ Opacè̤̌lya̤
Bínuôakhè̌ khwí Augusto nò̌ihtuô rǎmá plò́lò̌ kayǎ mwi̤ dố Romaké̤ tôké̤lè̤̌ cò́.
Yěma tè̤rǎmá plò́mwi̤ aré̤lố tôhû bí Quirino htwǒ khwídu dố Syria ké̤ akhè̌nuô hò́.
Rò kayǎ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ ka̤ lahyǎ dố adò̌, avǐ̤ rò ka̤sunuô̌ lahyǎ amwi̤.
Joseph o bí vǐ̤ Nazarè, Galilea ké̤kǔ nuô rò a htecuốkuô̌ dố vǐ̤ Bethelehem, Judaké̤, bí khwí Davi lé̤opacè̤̌lya̤ khǎlé̤nuô. Joseph ma Davi aklwǐalyǎ kalya̤ dǐtû́ tôprè̤ akhu-akhyě a ka̤kuô̌ bínuô.
È ná Maria dố a dyémá<sup>a</sup> htuô̌hò́ lǔ dố a ki phyé lǔ nuôtôprè̤ cuố benuô̌kuô̌ amwi̤. Bínuôakhè̌ ma Maria ohò́ ná ahò́athè́ hò́.
Rò bí èthǐ o pǎ bí vǐ̤ Bethelehem akhè̌nuô, Maria ahò́ tǒlè̌ hò́ dố a ki phúo hò́.
A phúoní̤ phúvyá̤prè̤́ prè̤khǔ tôprè̤ rò a phyáplû̌ lǔ ná ikè̤̌ rò a dya omyětǎ̤ lǔ dố pṳ́klókǔ, me̤těhérò hidò́kǔ dố agněnuô a o pǎ tôtó̤ to.
Tanémò́khuphú Ná Prè̤kyě̤thímíphú Tahe
Khǎlé̤ tavǐtava̤ bínuô tôphonuô, prè̤kyě̤thímíphú o tahe. Èthǐ hyǎ omyěpò̤́ ní̤dyé athímíphú tahe dố mi̤klè̌, dố nyelá̤khu tôpho.
Bínuôakhè̌ Byacè a tanémò́khuphú tôprè̤ hyǎ oluô̌htya pé̤ èthǐ, rò Byacè Cò́marya a tè̤lǐtè̤takhè̌ tahe lǐ tava̤ lò̌plǐ èthǐ rò èthǐ thè́isě taròthè́ lò̌plǐ cò́.
Manárò tanémò́khuphú hé èthǐ, “Thè́isě tǎmé̤! Vǎ phyéhyǎní̤ pé̤hò́ thǐ tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila dố a ki me̤ thè́krṳ̂̌ lakálakǒ cò́ ǔpwǒ̤꤮ prè̤ pǎ yěnuôhò́.
Yětôthè̌ dố Davi avǐ̤kǔ nuô, prè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ a Byacè má̤hò́ Krístu yě hyǎ o pacè̤̌lya̤ hò́.
Thǐ ki myáhtye pacè̤̌ tôprè̤ pǎ, rò ǔ phyáplû̌ lǔ ná ikè̤̌ rò ǔ be-omyětǎ̤ è dố pṳ́klókǔ nuô pǎ. Thǐ ki myáhtye phúnuôma má̤hò́ pacè̤̌phú dố vǎ hésoluô̌ pé̤ thǐ yěnuô tôprè̤ hò́.”
Bínuôakhè̌ tanémò́khuphú aklyěphú tômṳ hyǎoluô̌htya khyé tố̤kuô̌ ná tanémò́khuphú yětôprè̤ rò èthǐ irǒ htuthè́htya Cò́marya rò a irǒ lahyǎ,
“Me̤lǐme̤takhè̌ htuthè́htya lahyǎ Cò́marya dố a o dố khǎlé̤htyalô̌ tadûlố ǔ dố mò́khu yěnuô tôprè̤ pó꤮. Tè̤pě̤tè̤dwǒ ná tè̤kacṳ́kabè́ ki ohtya kuô̌dû dố hekhuyě rò a ki otố̤kuô̌dû ná kayǎ dố Cò́marya thè́plò oní̤ lǔ nuôtahe ní꤮.”
Bí tanémò́khuphú ka̤ kahtya htuô̌hò́ dố mò́khu akhè̌nuô, prè̤kyě̤thímí tahe hé ní̤dyé khyělǔ, “Cuố꤮, pè̤ cuố dố vǐ̤ Bethelehem rò pè̤ cuốmyákuô̌ tè̤htwǒhtya-ané̤ dố Byacè hyǎ dyéthè́gněkyǎ pè̤ tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yěnuô pó꤮.”
Rò èthǐ htecuố tapluố̤taplyě lahyǎ rò cuốmyáhtye Maria ná Joseph, htuô̌rò èthǐ cuốmyáhtye ǔ dya omyětǎ̤ pacè̤̌phú tôprè̤ dố pṳ́klókǔ.
Bí prè̤kyě̤thímíphú yětahe myáhtye pacè̤̌phú yě ná amuố̤aphè̌ akhè̌nuô, a cuố héluô̌ pé̤ ǔ phú tanémò́khuphú hésoluô̌kyǎ pé̤ èthǐ ná pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤ ari-akyǎ nuôtahe.
Lò̌꤮ kayǎ dố a ní̤huô̌ prè̤kyě̤thímíphú yětahe hésoluô̌ pé̤ lǔ tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yětahenuô a khyéthukhyéthè́ lò̌ lahyǎ cò́.
Maria tǒ̤maní̤ lò̌ tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yětahe rò a tane̤ ní̤dyé ari-akyǎ.
Prè̤kyě̤thímíphú yětahe ka̤khyě khyěthyá dố èthǐ thímí tahe a o. Rò phú tanémò́khuphú hésoluô̌ pé̤ èthǐ rò èthǐ ní̤huô̌nò́, èthǐ cuố myáhtyebènò́ akhu-akhyě, èthǐ htuthè́htya Cò́marya, htuô̌to èthǐ me̤lǐme̤takhè̌htya Cò́marya.
Bí pacè̤̌ yětôprè̤ bǎhtya hò́ athè̌ lwǐ̤thyó hò́rò a tǒbè dû́talí hò́ phá akhè̌nuô, èthǐ è́ ní̤dyé lǔmwi̤ ná Jesǔ phú tanémò́khuphú pó̤onekyǎ pé̤hò́ lǔmwǐ̤ bí amuố̤ muố̤dò̌ tyahí lǔ to akhè̌nuô.
Joseph Ná Maria Besǎsè̌ Jesǔ Dố Tè̤lǔtyǎ Hǒkǔ
Phú Mosè mekyǎ a tè̤thyótè̤thya ná èthǐ tǒbè me̤mwǒ̤plǐthǐplo lahyǎ ané̤nuô, ashuốkhè̌ hyǎtuố̤hò́. Rò thyáphú Joseph ná Maria ki besǎsè̌htya pacè̤̌phúyě dố Byacè anyěhyǎ nuôrò, èthǐ phyéní̤ pacè̤̌phúyě rò a cuố lahyǎ dố vǐ̤ Jerusalem.
(Phú Byacè tè̤thyótè̤thya tè̤rǎmárǎdyǎ o, “Lò̌꤮ phúvyá̤prè̤́ prè̤khǔ tahenuô tǒbè besǎsè̌htya è dố Byacè a mèthènyě.”)<sup>b</sup>
Phú Byacè héokyǎ a tè̤thyótè̤thya nuô, èthǐ tǒbè cuố lǔtyǎhtya kuô̌ “Htulwí̤thǒ nyě̤bè má̤torò htulwí̤ dǐkrǎ nyě̤bè.”<sup>c</sup>
Bínuôkhè̌, dố vǐ̤ Jerusalem akǔnuô kayǎ otôprè̤, amwi̤ ná Simeonè. È ma kayǎ cṳ̌e bezṳ̂́nyá̤ Cò́marya tôprè̤, htuô̌to Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè okuô̌ ná è. È ma kayǎ dố a opò̤́myásû̌ Cò́marya ki me̤lwóhteka̤ Israelphú dố tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ akǔ tôprè̤.
Htuô̌rò Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè dyémyáhtyelwó tǎ̤te̤ one hò́ è, a ki myáhtye tyahí Krístu dố Byacè Cò́marya nwóhtya lǔ yětôprè̤ híto hénuô, a bèthyění̤ híto.
Simeonè phyáhtya pacè̤̌phú dố a takhulo̤ rò a htuthè́htya Cò́marya rò a hé,
“Kố꤮ Byacè, phú nè̤ héone htuô̌hò́ nè̤ngó̤ nuô khǒnyá̤rò a lốhtyabǎhtya hò́, nò̌thyě kacṳ́kabè́ mo̤dû mò̌hò́ nè̤lulé má̤ vǎyě.
30-31 Nè̤ tè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ dố nè̤ taritaryǎ one pé̤ nè̤ kayǎ pwǒ̤prè̤ agně yěnuô, vǎ myáhtye shyěklò̤́ cò́hò́ ná vǎmèthè hò́.
È ma tè̤lǐ tômě dố a ki dyéluô̌htya pé̤ Judaphú má̤to tahe, htuô̌to a phyéhyǎní̤ pé̤ tè̤sò̌ri dố nè̤ myěcô Israelphú tahe a o.”
Dố Simeonè hébè tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yě akhu-akhyě, pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤ amuố̤aphè̌ khyéthukhyéthè́ nyacò́.
Simeonè sò̌ri htuô̌ èthǐ rò a hékyǎní̤ pacè̤̌phú amuố̤ Maria yěnuô, “Pacè̤̌yě Cò́marya nwóhtyahò́ lǔ dố a ki me̤lwóhteka̤ Israelphú tahe pǎ, rò a ki dyadudyahtyalô̌ kuô̌ke kayǎ dố aruô tahe pǎ. È ma Cò́marya a tè̤mátè̤dyǎ tôcô, rò kayǎ è́prè̤ ki hébè takhwótakèsû lǔ pǎ.
Phúnuôrò kayǎ è́prè̤ tane̤ dò́uốdò́bí tè̤ dố èthǐ athè́plòkǔ tahenuô, Cò́marya ki bámǒhtyaluô̌ pǎ” htuô̌rò a hé Maria, “Tè̤thè́plè̤̌nebè dố a htyǎ thyácò́ná nè́ nuô a ki prǒnuô̌ nè̤ thè́plò pǎ.”
Prè̤pro̤muố̤ okryá dố a muố̤prè̤́ nyacò́ hò́ o tôprè̤, amwi̤ ná Anna. È ma Phanuel aphúprè̤mò, è ma Asher myěcôphú tôprè̤. A phyéhtuô̌ avè̤ rò a otố̤ní̤ lǔ thuô̌thyótôna prè́.
Avè̤ thyěkyǎ lǔkhǎlé̤ rò a okryákyǎ ní̤dû prè́. Khǒnyá̤rò ana o hò́ shyělwǐ̤thyó ná lwǐ̤na hò́. A htecuố tôpho꤮ to, a oprè́ bí tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔnuô prè́. A cò́bucò́bè̌htya Cò́marya dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ mò̤́khíkhí mò̤́sè̌klè̌klè̌ cò́, htuô̌to a duôe sèesèǒ rò a kwǐcò́bè̌ pwǒ̤nyěpwǒ̤thè̌ cò́.
Bínuôkhè̌, a hyǎtuố̤ tǒtû́ dố èthǐ o rò a htuthè́htya Cò́marya. Htuô̌rò a hésoluô̌ pé̤ pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤ ari-akyǎ ná lò̌꤮ kayǎ dố a opò̤́myásû̌ Cò́marya ki me̤lwóhteka̤ vǐ̤ Jerusalemphú pǎ nuôtahe.
Joseph Ná Maria Ka̤khyě Khyěthyá Dố Vǐ̤ Nazarè
Bí Joseph ná Maria me̤htuô̌lò̌hò́ phú lò̌꤮ Byacè mekyǎ tè̤thyótè̤thya tahe akhè̌nuô, èthǐ ka̤khyě khyěthyá dố alé̤o ní̤dyé vǐ̤ Nazarè nuô. Vǐ̤yěnuô a o bí Galilea ké̤kǔ nuô.
Pacè̤̌yě a duhtya rò a hè̌shyoresò̌ hyǎ, rò a lốbǎ cò́ ná tè̤thíphè́ rò Cò́marya sò̌risò̌bǔní̤ lǔ.
Pacè̤̌ Jesǔ Dố Tè̤lǔtyǎ Hǒkǔ
Pwǒ̤nana꤮ bí ǔ me̤pwè̌me̤la ní̤dyé pwè̌ dố ǔ è́ ná tè̤cuốtalwópwè̌ akhè̌nuô, Jesǔ amuố̤aphè̌ cuốkuô̌ dố vǐ̤ Jerusalem.
Bí Jesǔ na ohò́ shyényě̤na akhè̌, amuố̤aphè̌ yěnuô, alé̤klǒ cuố lahyǎ tè̤cuốtalwópwè̌, rò a è́ cuốní̤ pacè̤̌phú Jesǔ.
Bí tè̤cuốtalwópwè̌ htuô̌hò́ akhè̌nuô, èthǐ ka̤khyě dố adò̌aso. Bínuôakhè̌, pacè̤̌ Jesǔ yě a okyǎ dố vǐ̤ Jerusalem akǔ, manárò amuố̤aphè̌ thè́gně to.
Èthǐ tane̤ ná a ka̤ tố̤kuô̌ hò́ ná kayǎ dố a cuốpwè̌ka̤ nuôtahe aklè̌ hò́. Bí èthǐ ka̤ htuô̌hò́ tônyě꤮ mò̤́hé akhè̌nuô, a myápṳ̌ sudyǎní̤ no Jesǔ dố aklwǐalyǎ tahe aklè̌ prè́.
Bí èthǐ myápṳ̌ rò a myáhtye pé̤ pǎ to akhè̌nuô, èthǐ ka̤khyě khyěthyá lahyǎ dố vǐ̤ Jerusalem.
Thuô̌nyětônyěnuô, a cuố myáhtyeno ná Jesǔ cuố o dố tè̤lǔtyǎ hǒkǔ prè́. A cuố onyǎo tố̤kuô̌ ná Juda a thárádu thǎmǎhtǔ tahe rò a cuốní̤dǎkuô̌ Cò́marya alǎ̤angó̤ tahe rò a hébèsudyǎ kuô̌ǔ bínuô.
Bí kayǎ lò̌꤮ plǐ ní̤huô̌ pacè̤̌phú yětôprè̤ a tè̤hébèhésû̌ akhè̌nuô, èthǐ khyéthukhyéthè́ lò̌plǐ cò́ a tè̤cyá̤tè̤dè ná a tè̤hésû ka̤khyě ǔ nuôtahe cò́.
Joseph ná Maria cuốmyáhtye lǔ rò a khyéthukhyéthè́ nyacò́, rò amuố̤ hé lǔ, “Phúkhǔ, nè̤ cuố me̤tuố̤ phúyě me̤tě? Vǎ ná nè̤phè̌ kṳ́kyǎ̤ rò myápṳ̌ lakǒ nè̤ ma tadû꤮ ké̤ cò́ meně.”
Rò pacè̤̌ Jesǔ hésû, “Thǐ cuố myápṳ̌ vǎ katè̤́ nuô me̤tě? Thǐ thè́gně nyǎ ná vǎ o dố vǎphè̌ ahikǔ to è̌.”
Manárò amuố̤aphè̌ thè́gněplǒ lǔ tè̤hébè yě angó̤lasá to.
Htuô̌rò pacè̤̌phúyě a krwǒ ka̤kuô̌khyě amuố̤aphè̌ dố vǐ̤ Nazarè rò a cṳ̌ muố̤lǎ̤phè̌ngó̤ pwǒ̤꤮ tôphuố. Amuố̤ tǒ̤ma oplò́lò̌ lò̌꤮ tè̤htwǒhtya ané̤ yěnuôtahe.
Jesǔ duhtya lốbǎ ná tè̤thítè̤phè́ rò Cò́marya ná prè̤lukayǎ myámo̤myádu ní̤dyé lǔ.
Giovanni Baptista A Tè̤hésodônyǎ
Bí Khwídu Tiberia pốtè̤ bǎhtya hò́ shyényǎ̤ na akhè̌nuô, Pontio Pilato htwǒhtya khwídu dố Judaké̤. Rò prè̤pố Galilea ké̤ ma Khwí Herodè. Rò Khwí Herodè apuố̤ Philipu ma prè̤pố Ituraea ké̤ ná Trakoniti ké̤. Khwí Lysania rò a pốní̤ ke Abilene ké̤.
Prè̤lǔtyǎ dulốǔ ma Anna ná Caipha hò́. Bínuôakhè̌ Zekaria aphúkhǔ Giovanni o dố ké̤sè̌htyěkya̤ lò̤́tamákhu rò Cò́marya hésoluô̌ tǎ̤pé̤ alǎ̤angó̤ dố Giovanni a o.
Phú Cò́marya alǎ̤angó̤ rǎone htuô̌hò́ dố Prè̤pro̤ Isaiah a likǔnuô, rò a hé,
“Kayǎ tôprè̤ è́htǒhtya dố ké̤sè̌htyěkya̤ lò̤́tamákhu rò a hé, ‘Taritaryǎ one lahyǎ klyá dố Byacè agně. Me̤cò́me̤pě̤ lahyǎ Byacè lé̤hyǎklyá agně tôbǒ ní꤮.
Lò̌꤮ ké̤tò̤kǔ tahenuô, bè thốbǎ lò̌. Lò̌꤮ khǒmǎ̤khǒlǒ ná sodusohtǔ tahenuô, bè me̤pě̤ lò̌. Me̤cò́ lò̌ klyá dố a takǐtaka̤ nuôtahe. Rò bè me̤thye lò̌ klyá dố a taprǐtaprú nuôtahe.
Kayǎ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ ki myáhtye lò̌ Cò́marya nwóhtya prè̤me̤lwóhteka̤ prè̤lu hekhuphú yěnuô tôprè̤ pǎ.’”<sup>a</sup>
Kayǎ tahe kíré̤ hyǎ plwǒ lahyǎ ané̤ ná htyě rò a hyǎró̤hyǎè́ nyacò́ dố Giovanni a o. Rò Giovanni hé èthǐ, “Rṳ́thíthǐ꤮! Maǔpě tôprè̤ dyérò̤dyéryě̤ thǐ ná thǐ ki siplè́bè́ ná Cò́marya a tè̤cirya dố a ki hyǎpǎ yěnuô pě?
Thǐ ki za̤ ní̤dû má̤lakǒ hò́ thǐné̤ hò́ kihérò dyéluô̌ lahyǎ thǐ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ tahe ná thǐ tè̤dya thǐ thè́plòthuôhtyě tahe. Héhtǒhélya̤ tǎ thǐné̤, ‘Pè̤ ma Abraham aklwǐalyǎ’ nuôtǎmé̤. Vǎ hé thǐ, Cò́marya me̤htwǒhtya lò̤́yětahe ná Abraham aphú má̤ a me̤cyá̤ prè́.
Kwǒ tôbè ohò́ dố thòkhǎshyéhò́ rò ǔ ki ikwǒ̤ khû́hò́ thòmò̤́ tahe pǎ, rò ǔ ki icǒtṳ̂̌ tuố̤ cò́ dố arwí̤ahtwo pǎ. Thòmò̤́ tômò̤́mò̤́ dố athèaphǒ twó̤ryá to nuô, ǔ ki ikwǒ̤ khû́kyǎ è pǎ rò ǔ ki vǐnuô̌kyǎ è dố mikǔ pǎ.”
Rò kayǎ è́prè̤ sudyǎ Giovanni, “Ki hé phúnuôrò pè̤ tǒbè me̤phútě?”
Rò a hésû èthǐ, “Kayǎ dố aca̤ o nyě̤pṳ̂nuô bè dyé pé̤ kuô̌ kayǎ dố aca̤ o kuô̌ǔ tôpṳ̂꤮ to nuôtahe. Htuô̌rò kayǎ dố a lé̤elé̤ǒ o tahenuô, iběeběǒ pé̤ kuô̌ǔ.”
Prè̤kwǐamo-arǎ tahe ki plwǒ kuô̌ lahyǎ ané̤ ná htyě rò a hyǎ dố Giovanni a o rò a hyǎ sudyǎ lǔ, “Thárá, pè̤ tǒbè me̤phútě?”
Rò a hésû èthǐ, “Kwǐ lahyǎ amo-arǎ phú ǔ nò̌kwǐ thǐnuô, kwǐlốkwǐklò̌ tǎ ná ǔ nò̌kwǐ thǐ nuô tǎmé̤.”
Klyěphú tahe sudyǎkuô̌ lǔ, “Pè̤kuô̌lé? Pè̤ tǒbè me̤phútě?”
Rò a hésû èthǐ, “Bè pṳ̂́phezè́plè́ ní̤ ǔrû̌ǔhtè̌ to. Kè̤bò̌kè̤bye tǎ ǔ tôprè̤꤮ tǎmé̤. Thè́plòmǐ ní̤ lahyǎ ná khwókè dố thǐ ní̤bè nuôtahe.”
Kayǎ è́prè̤ myásû̌ thè́lè̤ rò tane̤ lahyǎ Giovanni, “Taryá꤮ ma Krístu dố Cò́marya nwóhtya è dố a ki hyǎ me̤lwóhteka̤ prè̤lu hekhuphú hénuôma è cò́ hò́ kǒ꤮.”
Phúnuô akhu-akhyě Giovanni hé èthǐ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤, “Vǎ plwǒ thǐ ná htyě prè́, manárò prè̤ dố a taryěpro̤prya̤ shyosò̌ lốklò̌ cò́ ná vǎ tôprè̤nuô a ki hyǎ pǎ. Vǎ ilyě pé̤prè́ è khuphá plye̤ prè́ nuô꤮ vǎ kò ná è to. A ki hyǎ plwǒ thǐ ná Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè ná mi pǎ.<sup>b</sup>
È yěnuô athyáná kayǎ tôprè̤ dố a ikrè́sè́kyǎ buốthu ná buốsè́ nuô. Abuốsè́ tahenuô a ki ka̤klò̤̌plò́ dố acyǎkǔ pǎ, tadû́rò buốthu tahenuô a ki isû́û̌kyǎ ná mi dố a pǐ̤pé̤ cyá̤ pǎ tôphuố꤮ to yětôphè akǔ nuô pǎ.”
Giovanni hésodônyǎ pé̤ ǔ tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila dố klyá è́bǒ rò a dyéhè̌dyére ní̤dû kayǎ bè́mṳ nuôtahe.
Manárò Khwí Herodè yǒ cuốphyé ní̤dyé khyěthyádû akhǐ Herodia akhu-akhyě, Giovanni hé lǔ ná a me̤tè̤ yěnuôma a thû́. Htuô̌to dố aré̤khè̌nuô ma Khwí Herodè yǒ me̤ tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ tahe akhu-akhyě a dyapó̤ lǔ tè̤thû́ ná nuônuô.
Tû́yěnuô htuô̌to, Khwí Herodè me̤ tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ dulốpó̤ tôcô ma má̤hò́ a dò́tǎ̤kyǎ Giovanni dố htò̌kǔ yěnuô hò́.
Giovanni Plwǒ Pé̤ Jesǔ Htyě
Bí kayǎ bè́mṳ plwǒ htuô̌lò̌hò́ ané̤ ná htyě akhè̌nuô, Byacè Jesǔ plwǒ kuô̌ no htyě dố khyě. Bí a kwǐcò́bè̌ akhè̌nuô, mò́khu lṳmǒ ǎyǎhtya.
Htuô̌rò Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè klwo ané̤ phú htulwí̤ rò a hyǎ tǎ̤o dố lǔlo̤. Bínuôakhè̌ ngó̤pra̤tǎ̤ dố mò́khu rò a hé, “Nè̤ ma vǎphúkhǔ dố vǎ mo̤ ní̤dyé rò atǒabè ná vǎ thè́plòthuôhtyě tôprè̤.”
Jesǔ Aklwǐalyǎ Khǎshyékhǎrya̤ Tahe
Bí Jesǔ cáhtya ithyó ǔ akhè̌nuô, a na phûbǎ hò́ thuô̌shyě hò́. Ǔ tane̤tyá̤ lǔ ná Joseph aphú prè́.
Joseph ma Heli aphú,
Heli aphè̌ma Mathat, Mathat aphè̌ma Levi, Levi aphè̌ma Melchi, Melchi aphè̌ma Jannai, Jannai aphè̌ma Joseph,
