Tè̤hébè Ré̤ Dố Nyě
Paulu rǎ cuố pé̤ Ephesophú tahe ali yětôba akǔyěnuô, aré̤lố rò a dyéluô̌ pé̤ èthǐ, “Shyé꤮ shuốkhè̌ tǎ̤tǒtǎ̤bè hò́ pǎnuô, Cò́marya ki me̤lốme̤bǎ a tè̤taritaryǎ one yětahe pǎ. Lò̌꤮ tè̤dố a o dố mò́khu nuôtahe bèbè, lò̌꤮ a o dố hekhu yětahe nuôbèbè, a ki me̤plò́me̤cû̌ tố̤lò̌ lǔ dố a khuklò́dulố Krístu yětôprè̤ alè̤̌ pǎ.” (<a href="kyu-50-EPH-001.html#v10">1:10</a>). Htuô̌to a kwǐthè́zò̤ kuô̌ pó̤ Cò́marya akayǎ tahe ná a ki oplò́ocû̌ tố̤lǔ dố Cò́marya a tè̤taze-one dố adu-azǎ̤ yě alè̤̌ pǎ rò èthǐ ki o dǐtû́ lahyǎ ná thè́plò tômě꤮ cû̌ dố Krístu akǔ pǎ.
Li Epheso aré̤lố tôkwonuô, prè̤rǎli yětôprè̤ hésoluô̌ è́htya pé̤ pó̤ tè̤plò́tè̤cû̌ ari-akyǎ. A hé pé̤ ná Cò́marya nwóhtyaní̤ akayǎ tahe phútě, htuô̌rò dố aphúkhǔ Jesǔ Krístu akhu-akhyěrò Cò́marya plwǒkyǎ hò́ èthǐ tè̤thû́ phútě, rò a plwǒhte palǎ cuốkyǎ hò́ èthǐ phútě, htuô̌rò Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè thè́plòsukǔcwó̤ kuô̌ Cò́marya a tè̤ò́lya̤ dố adu-azǎ̤ yěnuô, phútěnuô, prè̤rǎli héluô̌htya phúnuô. Nyě̤kwo tôkwo kuô̌ke rò thyáphú prè̤hốli tahe ki krwǒ ohtwǒprè̤ ró̤lǔ tè̤tôcô꤮ tuô̌ dố Krístu akǔ tôprè̤ ná tôprè̤ agněnuôrò, a kwǐthè́zò̤ní̤ prè̤hốli tahe.
Cò́marya akayǎ tahenuô, a htwǒhtya hò́ tè̤tôcô꤮ tuô̌ hò́ ná Krístu phútěnuô a dyáluô̌ pé̤ ná ngó̤khákho tahe. A hé ná prè̤zṳ̂́etè̤ plò́mṳphú tahenuô athyáná kayǎ tôprè̤ ané̤klò̤́, Krístu rò athyáná kayǎ nuôtôprè̤ akhuklò́, má̤torò prè̤zṳ̂́etè̤plò́mṳ rò athyáná hi tômě, Krístu rò athyáná lò̤́ dố a lodulố ǔ tômě dố ǔ isò́lya̤ lǔ dố hihtûná̤, má̤torò prè̤zṳ̂́etè̤plò́mṳ rò athyáná mě, Krístu rò athyáná vè̤ a héklwo ngó̤ phúnuô. Paulu dônyǎ pé̤ ǔ ná Cò́marya abwídu-ataryěhtǔ dố Krístu akǔ yěnuôtahe ari-akyǎ. Lò̌꤮ Krístu a tè̤mo̤ ná Krístu a tè̤khyáthyě ané̤ dố krusulo̤ ná a tè̤plwǒkyǎ tè̤me̤thû́ ná Krístu abwídu-ataryěhtǔ ná a tè̤mwǒ̤plǐbǔphuố yětahe lò̌꤮ plǐ nuô, Paulu hésoluô̌ pé̤ lò̌ èthǐ ná tè̤ritè̤kyǎ yětahe.
