Tè̤hébwíhétaryě ná tè̤htuthè́htya 1:2-3:13
Dyéhè̌dyére Krístuphú tahe atè̤dya thè́plòthuôhtyě tahe 4:1-12
Ithyóithya ǔ ná Krístu ki hyǎ khyěthyá nyě̤phuốtôphuố ari-akyǎ 4:13-5:11
