Manárò thyáphú Cò́marya ki dyéluô̌htya Byacè Jesǔ Krístu a tè̤khyáthè́dǒ alốabǎ dố vǎlo̤ agněnuô, a thè́zò̤ní̤ vǎ. Me̤těhérò vǎ ma kayǎ dố a me̤tè̤thû́ dulốǔkhǒ tôprè̤ hò́. Thyáphú vǎ ki htwǒhtya pé̤ ǔ lé̤myábû̌ dố prè̤zṳ̂́e è dốkhyě tahe agně, htuô̌rò thyáphú èthǐ ki ní̤bèkuô̌ thè́htwǒprè̤ tacṳ́prè̤ talèkrè́ agně nuôrò Cò́marya thè́zò̤ní̤ vǎ prè́.
