Manárò prè̤mò tahehe nuô, a ki oklò̤sò́ma lahyǎ dố a tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ ná atè̤mo̤, ná a tè̤sǎsè̌ akǔ rò a ki o lahyǎ ná a tè̤dyathudyathè́ sǎprè̤́ ané̤ hénuôma, Cò́marya ki me̤lwóhteka̤ èthǐ bí èthǐ phúo akhè̌nuô pǎ.
