Tè̤hébè Ré̤ Dố Nyě
Li Jakomo yětôbanuô a rǎplò́rǎtố̤ è́lǎ tè̤ithyóithya dố tǒbè krwǒme̤ è tahe. Rò a rǎ cuố pé̤ lò̌꤮ Cò́marya akayǎ dố a cuố o pasǐ lò̌ dố hekhu yětôba akǔ. Thyáphú prè̤rǎliyě ki dyéluô̌ plǒryá pé̤ ǔ ná tè̤ithyóithya má̤hò́ tè̤thíphè́cyá̤dè, tè̤zṳ̌klyázṳ̌klǒ pé̤ Krístuphú atè̤dya thè́plòthuôhtyě ná a tè̤ihtòonyǎ yětahe ari-akyǎ, htuô̌rò a nò̌e è́lǎ ngó̤khákho tahe. Htuô̌rò kayǎduzá̤ ná kayǎsǒrya̤, tè̤ilo-ilyá, tè̤dyaryá thè́plòthuôhtyě, tè̤myádumyápatí, tè̤zṳ̂́ ná tè̤me̤, tè̤hébèhésû̌, tè̤thíphè́, tè̤klyétè̤ngǎ, tè̤phyéduné̤ ná tè̤shyalya̤ thè́plò, pṳ̌cirya ǔ, hébèhtuthè́, tè̤thè́plòhtǔ ná tè̤kwǐcò́bè̌ thǐ tahenuô, a hésoluô̌ pé̤ Krístuphú tahe a tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ ari-akyǎ.
Li yětôbanuô a ithyósò̌ pé̤ nyacò́ ǔ, Krístuphú a tè̤cò́bucò́bè̌ yě, tè̤me̤ tahe nuôma má̤hò́ tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ athèaphǒ hò́.
