Vǎ ma Jakomo, vǎ htwǒ Cò́marya ná Byacè Jesǔ Krístu a prè̤me̤tè̤phú tôprè̤. Vǎ hémo̤héryá cuố pé̤ Cò́marya akayǎ klwǐlyǎ shyényě̤muố̤ dố a cuốopasǐ sipryǎ lahyǎ dố khǎlé̤ pwǒ̤꤮ tôpho tahe a o.
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, bí thǐ myáhtye sítôbè ná tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤ilo-ilyá pwǒ̤꤮ tôcô hyǎbè thǐ akhè̌nuô, be è phú tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌ adu tôcô dố thǐgně nuô ní꤮.
Me̤těhérò, bí thǐ myáhtye sítôbè ná tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤ilo-ilyá me̤myá thǐ tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ yěakhè̌nuô, a dyéohtya è́klò̌lốpó̤ thǐ tè̤khyáthè́plòhtǔ tahe prè́nuô thǐ thè́gnědû hò́.
Thyáphú thǐ tè̤kahtòonyǎ yětahe ki yokalya̤ tó̤ tǎ taki꤮ tǎmé̤, thyáphú a kitǒkibè ná Cò́marya athè́plò, htuô̌to thǐ ki duhtya lốbǎkuô̌dû ná tè̤pwǒ̤꤮ tôcô agněnuô, thǐ tǒkò cyé̤pryě̤ khyáthè́plòhtǔ tuố̤ lahyǎ dố a tadû ní꤮.
Manárò dố thǐklè̌ nuô, kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ ki lobè tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè kihérò, a tǒkò kwǐhtya dố Cò́marya a o rò Cò́marya ki dyétǎ̤ dû è pǎ me̤těhérò, Cò́marya thè́prwǒ̤sû kayǎ dố a kwǐhtya lǔ nuô a otôprè̤꤮ to. A thè́zò̤ní̤ ǔ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤, rò a thè́zṳ̂́ dyé pé̤ ǔ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ cò́.
Manárò, bí thǐ kwǐcò́bè̌ akhè̌nuô, thǐ bè o ná tè̤zṳ̂́, rò thǐ tǒ thè́plòrarení̤ taki꤮ to. Kayǎ dố a thè́plòrare tahenuô, athyáná ké̤lathè́ hyǎ rò htyěháhó dố htyědutava̤ akǔ nuôtahe prè́.
7-8 Kayǎ dố athyáná htyěháhó yětahenuô, a ki ní̤bè tè̤ tôcôcô dố Byacè a o pǎ nuô, a tǒ tane̤ ní̤ to, me̤těhérò a me̤tè̤ ǐtětě꤮ nuô, athè́plò oè́ rò athè́plò lṳhtǒlṳlya̤ akhu-akhyě, a ní̤bè tè̤ tôcô꤮ to.
Kayǎ Sǒphásǒrya̤ Ná Kayǎ Duzá̤htyathè̌
Krístuphú dố a sǒphásǒrya̤ tôprè̤nuô, Cò́marya ki dyahtyalô̌ è pǎ, phúnuôrò a bè thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌.
Kayǎ duzá̤htyathè̌ dố Cò́marya shyatǎ̤ è tôprè̤nuô, a tǒbè thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ prè́, me̤těhérò kayǎ duzá̤htyathè̌ tahenuô a ki kuô̌tǎ̤thyěkyǎ thyáná mi̤thèvèphǒ nuôtahe pǎ.
Tamò̤́htya rò akṳ́lwókrǎ thyěkyǎ mi̤thè tahe akhu-akhyě, aphǒ tahe tǎ̤thyěkyǎ lò̌, rò a tè̤twó̤tè̤ryá tahe sǐmé̤kyǎ lò̌ prè́. Phúnuôhò́ bí kayǎ duzá̤htyathè̌ tahe cuố me̤kuố̤me̤khá tè̤ akhè̌pǎnuô, a ki thyěkyǎ kuô̌dû phúnuô pǎ.
Tè̤ce̤myá Ná Tè̤ilo-ilyá
Kayǎ dố a khyáthè́plòhtǔ tahenuô, shyé꤮ a myáhtye sítôbè ná tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤ilo-ilyá akhè̌pǎnuô, a ki ní̤bè tè̤sò̌ri pǎ, me̤těhérò bí èthǐ me̤pé̤kyǎ htuô̌hò́ tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤ilo-ilyá phúyě akhè̌nuô, Cò́marya ki dyé èthǐ tè̤htwǒprè̤ tacṳ́prè̤ ashyězṳ́ dố a ò́lya̤ ná a ki dyé kayǎ dố a mo̤ní̤ lǔ nuôtahe pǎ.
Kayǎ dố a myáhtye sítôbè tè̤ilo-ilyá phúyě tahenuô, a tǒbè héní̤, “Tè̤yěma a o dố Cò́marya a o hyǎ prè́,” a bè héní̤ phúnuô to. Tè̤ilo-ilyá mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ nuô a ilohtò́cwibè́ pé̤ ná Cò́marya to. Htuô̌to Cò́marya ané̤byacè ní̤dûnuô, a ilo-ilyá ná ǔ tôprè̤꤮ to.
Manárò bí kayǎ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ myáhtye sítôbè ná tè̤ilo-ilyá akhè̌nuô, ané̤klò̤́ a tè̤thè́zṳ̂́ mǔmyá̤ ní̤dû nuôtahe cwiní̤htò́ní̤ dyédû lǔ prè́.
Dốkhyěrò bí kayǎ yětôprè̤ me̤hò́ a tè̤thè́zṳ̂́ mǔmyá̤ yěakhè̌nuô, a dyéhtwǒhtya lǔ tè̤thû́, yětôphuốrò tè̤thû́ yě pốtaríní̤ lò̌plǐ hò́ lǔthè́plò rò aphúolya̤ ní̤dyéhò́ tè̤thyě tacṳ́prè̤ hò́.
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ dố vǎ mo̤ní̤ thǐ꤮, tè̤ dố a tǒto tahenuô, cuốzṳ̂́e tǎ lahyǎ tǎmé̤ ní꤮.
Lò̌꤮ shyězṳ́ dố aryá rò a lốbǎ nuôma Cò́marya dố a byálya̤ tamò̤́ ná sè ná lè̌ yětahe tôprè̤ dyétǎ̤ prè́. Cò́marya alé̤klǒ htulya taplekhókyǎ kuô̌ phú tè̤lǐ zo̤uô htulya khókyǎ nuôto.
Dố pè̤ ní̤huô̌ tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila tè̤má̤tè̤cò́ akhu-akhyěrò Cò́marya dyéhtwǒhtya hò́ pè̤ ná aphú cṳ́꤮ dû phú athè́plò ní̤dû nuôhò́. Thyáphú pè̤ ki htwǒhtya thòthè dố athè ré̤lố ǔ tahe dố tè̤byálya̤ lò̌꤮ plǐ yětahe aklè̌ nuôrò, a dyéhtwǒhtya hò́ pè̤ ná aphú prè́.
Tè̤ní̤dǎ Ná Tè̤cṳ̌e
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ dố vǎ mo̤ní̤ thǐ꤮, tǒ̤ní̤ lahyǎ ngó̤ yětômû̌ ní꤮. Kayǎ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ tǒbè ní̤dǎ tǎ̤te̤, a tǒbè tane̤hébè lahyǎ rò a tǒbè thè́plòduhtya pryǎ ní̤ to.
Me̤těhérò, kayǎ dố thè́plòdu thuôhtyěhtǔ tahenuô, a dyéhtwǒhtya cyá̤ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ acò́ate̤ dố Cò́marya thè́zṳ̂́ nò̌ohtwǒprè̤ yěnuô takhyá꤮ to.
Phúnuôrò vǐkyǎ lò̌plǐ tè̤thè́zò̤́thè́ryǎ̤ dố thǐ me̤ tamǒmǒ ènuôtahe ná lò̌꤮ thǐ lé̤klǒ dố a mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ nuôtahe. Rò shyalya̤ lahyǎ thǐ thè́plò rò ní̤dǎ zṳ̂́e kuô̌ lahyǎ Cò́marya alǎ̤angó̤ dố a isò́iplû̌tǎ̤ dố thǐ thè́plòkǔ yěnuôtahe. Alǎ̤angó̤ yěnuôma a me̤lwóhteka̤ bè́cyá̤ thǐ.
Thǐ ní̤dǎ prè́tû́ Cò́marya alǎ̤angó̤ rò thǐ ki cṳ̌e krwǒme̤kuô̌ phú a hénuô to hénuôma thǐ lahǒ lya̤ ní̤dyédû hò́ thǐné̤ hò́. Thǐ tǒbè ní̤dǎ krwǒme̤ kuô̌ phú Cò́marya alǎ̤angó̤ hénuô.
Kayǎ dố a ní̤dǎ cò́cû́ prè́ Cò́marya angó̤ rò a krwǒme̤ kuô̌ǔ to tahe nuôma athyáná kayǎ dố a dômyá ní̤dyé amèthè ná mǎ̤duô tahe nuôprè́.
A myá ní̤dyé htuô̌ ané̤ ná mǎ̤duô rò a htecuố taphǎkyǎ akhè̌, lò̌꤮ a myáhtye dố mǎ̤duôkǔ nuôtahe, a sǒtapa̤kyǎ tôphuố sǒtapa̤ prè́.
Tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila ma Cò́marya a tè̤thyótè̤thya dố alốabǎ rò a me̤lwóhteka̤ kayǎ dố tè̤thû́tè̤ora akǔ. Kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ dố a pṳ̌thè́gně tǎ̤te̤ryá tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila yě rò a sǒtapa̤kyǎ tè̤ithyóithya yě to tahe, htuô̌to a ní̤dǎ krwǒme̤ tè̤ithyóithya yětôprè̤nuô, Cò́marya ki sò̌ri atè̤me̤ yěnuô pǎ.
Kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ dố a tane̤lya̤ ní̤dyé ané̤ ná è ma kayǎ cò́bucò́bè̌ ryá nyacò́ tè̤ tôprè̤, tadû́rò a ki rò̤ní̤dyé a tè̤hébè to hénuô, a cò́bucò́bè̌ ryá tè̤ yěnuô, angṳdupri̤du pǎ tôcô꤮ to, rò è htwǒ prè́ kayǎ dố a lahǒlahya lya̤ ní̤dyé ané̤ tôprè̤ prè́.
Tè̤cò́bucò́bè̌ dố Phè̌ Cò́marya dya hò́ ná tè̤ dố a mwǒ̤plǐ lốlốbǎbǎ tahe nuôma má̤hò́ tè̤myákhwèní̤ phúokryáohtû̌ tahe ná prè̤mòokryá dố a tuố̤bè ná tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tahe, htuô̌to kayǎ dố a khò̌pé̤ ní̤dyé ané̤ rò a otaphǎye̤bè́ ná hekhu a tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ thǐ nuôtahe hò́.
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, thǐ ma kayǎ dố a zṳ̂́enyá̤e Byacè Jesǔ Krístu dố a o ná tè̤lǐtè̤takhè̌ tôprè̤ tahe. Phúnuô akhu-akhyě, thǐ tǒbè myádu myápatí ní̤ ǔ tôprè̤꤮ to.
Kayǎ duzá̤ tôprè̤ rò thǐ è́sû bezṳ̂́benyá̤ lǔ, htuô̌to dố thǐklè̌ tôprè̤nuô a hé lǔ, “Onyǎo dố khuklyáhtyalô̌ ryá akhuyě” rò a hé kuô̌ke kayǎ sǒphásǒrya̤ nuôtôprè̤, “Kahtò obínuô,” má̤torò “Onyǎo bí two̤khu bí vǎ khǎduô khǎshyéyě,” a hé phúnuô.
Thǐ me̤kryá꤮ ǐtě nuôma thǐ thè́gně ní̤dyé to è̌? Kayǎ dố thǐklè̌ yětahenuô, thǐ myáhtye khó èthǐ rò thǐ htwǒhtya prè̤cirya ǔ dố a oná tè̤tane̤ mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ thǐtahe hò́.
Puố̤vyá̤mo̤ thǐ꤮, ní̤dǎ lahyǎ. Kayǎ dố a sǒphásǒrya̤ dố hekhu yětahe nuôma, thyáphú èthǐ tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ kishyokisò̌htya rò èthǐ ki me̤ní̤ htyěké̤ dố Cò́marya ò́lya̤ one pé̤ kayǎ dố a mo̤ní̤ lǔ nuôtahe agněnuôrò, Cò́marya nwóhtya èthǐ hò́ nuôma thǐ thè́gně tǎ̤te̤ dû hò́.
Manárò kayǎ sǒphásǒrya̤phú tahenuô thǐ bezṳ̂́benyá̤ ní̤ kuô̌ èthǐ to. Kayǎ dố a pé̤epé̤ǒ me̤cyě̤me̤cṳ̂ thǐ nuôma kayǎ duzá̤htyathè̌phú tahenuô prè́. Prè̤ dố a cwihyǎ thǐ dố prè̤ciryatè̤phú tahe a mèthènyě nuôma èthǐ nuôtahe hò́.
Kayǎ dố a pacyé̤ishyé pyélò̌ Krístu mwi̤twó̤mwi̤ryá dố ǔ dyé htuô̌hò́ thǐ yěnuôma má̤ èthǐ nuôtahe hò́.
Lisǎsè̌kǔ hé, “Mo̤ní̤ ǔruô phú nè̤ mo̤lya̤ ní̤dyé nè̤né̤ nuô,”<sup>a</sup> a hé phúnuô. Thǐ ki cṳ̌e má̤lakǒ Cò́marya ahtyěké̤ atè̤thyótè̤thya yě hénuôma thǐ me̤tǒhò́ tè̤ hò́.
Manárò thǐ ki myádu myápatí ǔ hénuôma, thǐ me̤hò́ tè̤thû́ rò tè̤thyótè̤thya cirya hò́ thǐ phú kayǎ me̤thû́ tè̤thyótè̤thya tôprè̤nuô hò́.
Ǔpě꤮ tôprè̤ bèbè a ki me̤thû́ tè̤mekyǎngó̤ tômû̌ hénuô, a me̤thû́ lò̌hò́ tè̤mekyǎngó̤ lò̌꤮ plǐ hò́.
Cò́marya hé, “Cuốthû́ tǎ prè̤mòprè̤khǔ tǎmé̤” a hé phúnuô. Htuô̌rò a hékuô̌ pó̤, “Me̤thyě tǎ kayǎ tǎmé̤” a hé pó̤ phúnuô. Phúnuôrò thǐ ki cuốthû́ prè̤mòprè̤khǔ to tadû́rò thǐ ki me̤thyě kayǎ hénuô, thǐ htwǒhtya hò́ kayǎ dố a me̤thû́ tè̤thyótè̤thya tôprè̤ hò́.<sup>b</sup>
Rò̤ní̤ lahyǎ thǐ tè̤hébè ná thǐ tè̤me̤ tahenuô me̤těhérò tè̤thyótè̤thya dố a dyé pé̤ kayǎ tè̤palǎ yě ki cirya thǐ pǎ.
Me̤těhérò kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ dố a thè́zò̤ kuô̌ǔ to nuô, shyé꤮ Cò́marya cirya kayǎ nuôtôprè̤ akhè̌pǎnuô, a thè́zò̤ ní̤kuô̌ lǔ to pǎ. Tè̤thè́zò̤ní̤ ǔ nuô a me̤pé̤ tè̤cirya.
Tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ Ná Tè̤me̤
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ ki hé ná vǎ tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ o a hé tadû́rò a ki dyéluô̌ a tè̤zṳ̂́yě ná a me̤ tè̤ryá tahe to hénuô, abwíataryě o tôcô꤮ to. A tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ yěnuô a me̤siplè́cyá̤ lǔ to.
Hékuốré̤ thǐ puố̤vyá̤ prè̤khǔ má̤torò thǐ puố̤vyá̤ prè̤mò tôprè̤prè̤ nuô a lé̤kû̌lé̤thyá, a lé̤elé̤ǒ tônyě ná tônyě agně ki olốobǎ to hébyenuô,
rò dố thǐklè̌ tôprè̤prè̤nuô a ki hé lǔ, “Ka̤mo̤mo̤ ka̤ryáryá ní꤮, Cò́marya ki okuô̌ dû ná nè̤ pǎ, me̤lè̤ryání̤ nè̤né̤ ní, rò ekò́ǒbǎ dû lahyǎ ní꤮,” a hé phúnuô tadû́rò thǐ ki dyépé̤ èthǐ lé̤kû̌lé̤thyá, lé̤elé̤ǒ tôcô꤮ to hénuô, abwíataryě o tôcô꤮ to.
Tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ nuôma a thyáphú nuôhò́. A ki oprè́tû́ tè̤zṳ̂́ tôcôtuô̌, tè̤me̤ ki oluô̌ kuô̌to hénuôma má̤prè́ tè̤zṳ̂́ dố a thyě prè́.
Hékuốré̤ kayǎ tôprè̤ ki hé, “Kayǎ tahehe nuô a o ná tè̤zṳ̂́, tahehe rò a o ná tè̤me̤ryá tè̤.” Ki hé rò vǎ ki hésû è, dyéluô̌ pé̤ vǎ nè̤ tè̤zṳ̂́ dố a sǒdǒ ná tè̤me̤ yěnuô, rò vǎ ki dyéluô̌ pé̤ kuô̌ke nè̤ ná vǎ tè̤zṳ̂́ dố a o ná tè̤me̤yě pǎ vǎ ki hésû è phúnuô.
Nè̤ zṳ̂́e ná Byacè Cò́marya otû́ tôprè̤꤮ tuô̌. Aryáhò́. Khǐnékhǐnò̌ tahe cò́nuô a zṳ̂́e thyákuô̌dû phúnuônuô, htuô̌to èthǐ zṳ̂́e rò a thè́isě tanyǎ̤tadè cò́.
Kayǎ olốoklò̌, tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ dố a o ná tè̤me̤ to tahe nuôma a olốoklò̌ prè́ nuôma, nè̤ thè́zṳ̂́ myáhtye è̌?
Pè̤phè̌ Abraham dố꤮ nyénu tôprè̤nuô Cò́marya dyacò́dyate̤ è phútě? A ní̤dǎ Cò́marya angó̤ rò bí a lǔhtya aphúkhǔ Isaac dố tè̤lǔrè̤́khu akhè̌nuô, Cò́marya dyacò́dyate̤ lǔ ná a tè̤me̤yě akhyě prè́.
Nè̤ myáhtye hò́ atè̤zṳ̂́ ná a tè̤me̤yě me̤ró̤lǔ tè̤hò́. A tè̤me̤yě a me̤ lốbǎ pé̤hò́ lǔ tè̤zṳ̂́ hò́.
Rò lisǎsè̌ héo yěnuô a lốbǎhyǎ hò́ rò a hé, “Abraham zṳ̂́e Cò́marya rò dố atè̤zṳ̂́ akhu-akhyě, Cò́marya dyahò́ lǔ phú kayǎcò́kayǎte̤ tôprè̤ nuôhò́,”<sup>c</sup> a hé phúnuô. Phúnuôrò Abraham nuô ǔ è́ lǔ ná Cò́marya a khǒbò́thyó.
Phúnuôrò, thǐ myáhtyehò́ ná Cò́marya dyacò́dyate̤ kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤nuô, a dyacò́dyate̤ tû́prè́ lǔ ná a tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ yětôcô prè́ nuô má̤to. A dyacò́dyate̤ lǔ ná atè̤me̤ dố a dyéluô̌ ná a o ná a tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ yěnuô prè́.
Himyáphèmuố̤ Rahab nuôma a thyáphúnuô hò́. Thyáphú Israelphú dố a nuô̌ htû́myá huô tè̤ nuôtahe ki htecuốsiplè́ bè́kyǎ ná klyá dố aruô tôbǒ agněnuô, a è́mo̤sû èthǐ rò a me̤cwó̤ pé̤ èthǐ akhu-akhyě Cò́marya dyacò́dyate̤ lǔ ná a tè̤phyétè̤me̤ yěakhyěhò́.
Phúnuôhò́, tè̤zṳ̂́ dố a o ná tè̤me̤ tonuô, athyáná né̤klò̤́ dố thè́plòhtwǒprè̤ o kuô̌ dố lǔlo̤ to rò a thyěkyǎ nuô hò́.
Pli̤ Ari-akyǎ
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, thǐ tǒ htwǒ ró̤è́ Thárá to, me̤těhérò phú thǐ thè́gně htuô̌dûnuô hò́, pè̤ dố a htwǒ Thárá tahenuô, Cò́marya ki cirya sò̌klò̌ pè̤ ná kayǎ dố aruô nuôtahe pǎ.
Pè̤ me̤thû́ ka̤khyěhyǎnyě lò̌plǐ tè̤ pwǒ̤꤮ tôprè̤ hò́. Manárò kayǎ dố a hébèthû́nò́ kuô̌ǔ tôphuố꤮ to tôprè̤nuô, è má̤ hò́ kayǎ dố alốabǎ tôprè̤ rò arò̤aryě̤bè́ ní̤dyé lò̌hò́ a né̤sǐprè̤ hò́.
Thyáphú tathí ki cṳ̌e pè̤ngó̤nuô rò, pè̤ nò̌ a̤ma tathí ná tò̤́htè́plye̤, rò pè̤ tarícuốbè́ lò̌ tathísǐduô̌.
Kayǎpli̤ nuôma a thyáphú nuôhò́. A patíphú prè́ tadû́rò a hébèhtuthè́ dyálốdyáklò̌ ní̤dyé atè̤me̤ ari-akyǎ tahe. Tane̤myámò̌, tanò̌tahǒ ducò́ bátě꤮ bèbè, mi̤phǒsèphú tôsè prè́nuô a û̌lò̌bè́ pé̤ prè́.
Kayǎ pli̤nuô athyáná mi nuôhò́. Dố né̤klò̤́ krṳ̂krò̤̌ aklè̌nuô, pli̤ ma athyáná hekhu dố a lốbǎ ná tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ yětôba nuôhò́. A me̤thò̌ lò̌hò́ kayǎ ané̤klò̤́ sǐprè̤ hò́. Pli̤yě a isû́û̌ lò̌lá̤ taklikyǎ lò̌ cò́ pè̤ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ ná miyě hò́ rò mi yěnuôma a o dố mò́rapò̤tya̤ akǔ hyǎ hò́.
Prè̤lu hekhuphú me̤nya̤cyá̤ lò̌ tè̤phútè̤lye̤ pwǒ̤tôcô, a me̤nya̤cyá̤ lò̌ tè̤mi̤tè̤myá̤ tahe, htu tahe, rṳ́ tahe ná tè̤̌ tahe lò̌꤮ plǐ cò́.
Manárò kayǎ dố a me̤nya̤ bè́cyá̤ kayǎpli̤ yěnuô a o tôprè̤꤮ to. Kayǎpli̤ yěnuô a lốbǎ cò́ ná tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ tahe cò́ rò ǔ pốbè́cyá̤ lǔ to, a o lốbǎ cò́ ná atè̤ryǎ̤ dố a me̤thyěme̤mé̤ ǔ tahe.
Thǐ thè́gně ná pè̤ nò̌e pè̤pli̤ yěnuô ná lé̤htuthè́htya pè̤ Phè̌ Byacè Cò́marya, htuô̌to pè̤ nò̌e kuô̌ pó̤ è ná pè̤ lé̤isò̌hǎ kayǎ dố Cò́marya byálya̤ è phú ané̤klò̤́ yěnuôtahe.
Dố kyǎ̤kǔ tôkǔkǔ꤮ tuô̌prè́ yěakǔnuô tè̤htuthè́htya rò a htehte, tè̤isò̌hǎ tahe rò a htehte. Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, a tǒkò hte phúnuô to.
Htyěhtekhu tôkǔkǔ꤮ tuô̌prè́ akǔ nuô, htyětabè́ rò a htwíhtehte, htyěkhè rò a htwíhtehte, a htwíhte tố̤lǔ phúnuôma aní̤ nyǎ è̌?
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, kadwímò̤́ thèhtecyá̤ olivathè to. Thòbǐthèmò̤́ thè́htecyá̤ kadwíthè to, phúnuôhò́ htyěhtekhu dố akhè tôkǔnuô, a nò̌htwíhte cyá̤kuô̌ htyětabè́ to.
Tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè O Dố Mò́khu Hyǎ
Kayǎ dố thǐklè̌ tôprè̤prè̤ dố a o ná a tè̤tane̤ cyá̤dè rò a thè́gně tǎ̤plú nuôma ǔpě? A tǒbè dyéluô̌ atè̤ yětahenuô ná a tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ dố aryá, htuô̌to a tǒbè dyéluô̌ a me̤tè̤ yěnuô ná dố tè̤shyalya̤ thè́plò. Tè̤shyalya̤ yěnuôma a hyǎ dǐtû́ dố tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè yěnuô a o prè́.
Manárò dố thǐ thè́plòkǔnuô, thǐ ki thè́kháthè́hte nyacò́ lǔ, thǐ mo̤lya̤ ní̤dyé thǐné̤ rò thǐ myádulya̤ ní̤dyé thǐné̤ yětahe ki o hénuô, hébè htuthè́ ní̤dyé tǎ thǐné̤ ná thǐ o ná tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè phúnuô tǎmé̤, rò me̤takèsû tǎ tè̤má̤tè̤cò́ yěnuô tǎmé̤.
Tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè phúnuôtahe ma a o dố mò́khu hyǎ má̤to, hekhuné̤khu a tè̤tane̤ cyá̤dè nuôtaheprè́. Tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè phúnuôtahe ma a o dố Thè́ Sǎsè̌ Byacè a o hyǎ má̤to, a o dố khǐnékhǐnò̌ a o hyǎ prè́.
Bí tè̤thè́kháthè́hte lǔ, tè̤mo̤lya̤ ní̤dyé né̤ rò myádulya̤ ní̤dyé né̤ tahe o akhǎlé̤ nuô, thǐ ki myáhtye tè̤me̤tarû̌tapyǎ ná tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ pwǒ̤꤮ tôcô ki ohtya bínuô pǎ.
Manárò tè̤tane̤cyá̤dè dố a o dố mò́khu hyǎ hénuôma a mwǒ̤plǐ ré̤lố pǎ, htuô̌pǎrò a dyé ohtyadû tè̤mo̤tè̤pě̤, tè̤tane̤ cyá̤pé̤ dố ǔgně, thè́plòo ní̤dǎ ǔ tè̤hébè, lốbǎ ná tè̤thè́zò̤ ná me̤tè̤ryá tahe, myádu myápatí ǔ to, htuô̌rò tè̤cyé̤ me̤kháme̤kho tahe o to.
Kayǎ dố a dyéohtya tè̤pě̤tè̤dwǒ nuô, a isò́iplû̌ hò́ tè̤mo̤tè̤pě̤ aklwǐalwí rò shyé꤮ ǔ kè́ka̤dwóhò́ è akhè̌pǎnuô, a ki ní̤bè tè̤cò́tè̤te̤ athè pǎ.
Krístuphú Cṳ̌e Cò́marya Pwǒ̤꤮ Phuố
Tè̤krékryá̤ lǔ tahe ná tè̤klyétè̤ngǎ lǔ tahenuô a cuố hyǎnuô̌ tuố̤dố thǐklè̌ phútě? A hyǎnuô̌ phútě hénuôma, a hyǎnuô̌ dố thǐ thè́plò a tè̤thè́zṳ̂́ mǔmyá̤ tahe sátè̤ dố thǐkǔ yěnuô tahe a o hò́.
Thǐ thè́zṳ̂́ tè̤ rò thǐ ní̤bèto akhu-akhyě thǐ me̤thyě kayǎ. Thǐ thè́zṳ̂́thè́lò̌ tè̤ rò thǐ ní̤bècyá̤ tè̤tôcô꤮ to akhu-akhyě, thǐklyéthǐngǎ khyělǔ. Thǐ kwǐ kuô̌ǔ Cò́marya to akhu-akhyě, thǐ thè́zṳ̂́ tè̤ tahe rò thǐ ní̤bè cyá̤ kuô̌ǔ to.
Rò bí thǐ kwǐ tè̤ akhè̌, thǐ ní̤bè kuô̌ǔ tôcô꤮ to, me̤těhérò thǐ thè́plò a tè̤taze-one thè́zṳ̂́kwǐ tahenuô, a lṳthû́ lahyǎ prè́. Thǐ kwǐ lahyǎ prè́ ná thǐ thè́zṳ̂́ nò̌e è ná thǐ lé̤me̤mo̤lya̤ ní̤dyé thǐné̤ agně prè́ nuô̌.
Kayǎ dố a thè́plòka dố Cò́marya akhu thǐ꤮, thǐ bò́thyó ná hekhu a tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ tahe nuôma thǐ htwǒhtyahò́ prè̤ dố a thè́hte Cò́marya tahehò́ nuôma thǐ thè́gně to è̌? Kayǎ dố a thè́zṳ̂́ htwǒhtya hekhu a tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ yětahe a khǒbò́thyó tôprè̤prè̤nuô a me̤ thè́htethè́hǎ hò́ ané̤ ná Cò́marya hò́.
Cò́marya hé tè̤ dố lisǎsè̌kǔ tahenuô, angó̤lasá oto bè tane̤ní̤ phúnuô tôprè̤꤮ to. Lisǎsè̌kǔ hé, “Cò́marya be-o thè́htwǒprè̤ dố pè̤kǔ yěnuô, a thè́zṳ̂́ nò̌htwǒ ná atè̤ rò a thè́khwè́ ní̤dyé nyacò́.”<sup>a</sup>
Manárò tè̤bwítè̤taryě dố Cò́marya dyétǎ̤ pè̤ yěnuô, ahè̌are shyolố klò̌pǎ cò́. Phúnuô akhu-akhyě lisǎsè̌kǔ hé,
“Cò́marya me̤tǎ̤tṳ̂̌ sûkyǎ kayǎ dố a dyahtyalô̌ athè́plò nuôtahe, manárò abwíataryě yěnuô a dyétǎ̤ è́lốklò̌ dố kayǎ dố a shyalya̤ athè́plò nuôtahe alo̤.”<sup>b</sup>
Phúnuôrò shyalya̤ lahyǎ thǐ thè́plò dố Cò́marya alè̤̌, rò sásû khǐnéricyá̤ khuklò́ nuô tû́ma khǐnéricyá̤ khuklò́ ki klya cuố taphǎkyǎ dố thǐo pǎ.
Thò́thû́ hyǎphû lahyǎ thǐné̤ ná Cò́marya tû́ma a thò́thû́ hyǎphûkuô̌ ané̤ ná thǐ prè́. Prè̤oraphú thǐ꤮, sǐplǐkyǎ lahyǎ thǐ takhunuô. Kayǎ thè́plò oè́ thǐ꤮, me̤mwǒ̤plǐkyǎ lahyǎ thǐ thè́plònuô.
Thè́plè̤̌nebè mò̌ lahyǎ, nguố̤hè mò̌ lahyǎ. Thǐ tè̤nyě̤hǎ yěnuô htulyakyǎ è ná thǐ tè̤nguố̤tè̤hè yěnuô, thǐ tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌ yěnuô htulya kyǎmò̌ è ná thǐ tè̤thè́plè̤̌ yěnuô.
Shyalya̤ lahyǎ thǐ thè́plò dố Byacè a mèthènyě rò a ki dyahtyalô̌dû thǐ pǎ.
Dya Tè̤thû́ Hémǔmyá̤ Tǎ Prè̤zṳ̂́etè̤phú Tahe Tǎmé̤
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, hémǔmyá̤ ní̤dyé tǎ lǔ tôprè̤ ná tôprè̤ tǎmé̤ ní꤮. Ǔpěpě꤮ bèbè dố a hémǔmyá̤ kayǎ dố a zṳ̂́e Krístu tôprè̤prè̤ má̤torò a dya tè̤thû́ kayǎ dố a zṳ̂́e Krístu tôprè̤prè̤ nuôma má̤hò́ a hébè mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ hò́ tè̤thyótè̤thya rò a dya tè̤thû́ hò́ tè̤thyótè̤thya yěnuô hò́. Thǐ ki dya tè̤thû́ tè̤thyótè̤thya yěnuô hérò, thǐ ma kayǎ dố a cṳ̌e tè̤thyótè̤thya má̤to. Má̤prè́ kayǎ dố a dya tè̤thû́ tè̤thyótè̤thya prè́.
Dyahtyalô̌ Tǎ Thǐ Thè́plò Tǎmé̤
Khǒnyá̤yě ní̤dǎ lahyǎ, dố thǐklè̌ tahehenuô a hé lahyǎ, “Yětônyě tomaná shyéparǒ pǎ nuô, pè̤ ki cuố dố vǐ̤tôvǐ̤ pǎ rò pè̤ ki cuố o bínuô tôna pǎ. Rò pè̤ ki cuố pṳ̌ me̤kuố̤me̤khá rò me̤kuố̤ è́htyalốklò̌ pó̤ ná amuố̤rǎ yěnuôpǎ.”
Parǒpǎ thǐ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ kíré̤ me̤phútě pǎ nuô, thǐ thè́gně to. Thǐ tè̤ohtwǒprè̤ yěnuôma athyáná ǐtě? Athyáná tè̤khuôhtya dố a oluô̌ taplô̤phú rò a lamé̤kyǎ khyě nuôprè́.
Thǐ tǒkò hé lahyǎ phútě hérò, “Byacè ki thè́plòo ná pè̤ ki ohtwǒprè̤ pǎ hérò pè̤ ki me̤ phúyěphúnuô pǎ,”
manárò khǒnyá̤yě thǐ dyahtyalô̌ lahyǎ thǐ thè́plò rò thǐ hébè htyamò́htyapho ní̤dyé lahyǎ thǐné̤. Lò̌꤮ tè̤dyahtyalô̌ thè́plò phúnuô tahema tè̤mǔmyá̤ricyá̤ prè́.
Phúnuôrò kayǎ dố a thè́gně ná a tǒkò me̤ tè̤ryá yě tadû́rò a ki me̤to tahenuô, a me̤hò́ tè̤thû́hò́.
Tè̤dyérò̤dyéryě̤ One Kayǎ Duzá̤ Tahe
Kayǎduzá̤ thǐ꤮ khǒnyá̤rò ní̤dǎ lahyǎ tè̤ dố vǎ kíré̤ héso pé̤ thǐ yě. Tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ kíré̤ hyǎbèhò́ thǐ akhu-akhyě nguố̤hè onemò̌ lahyǎ.
Thǐ tè̤duzá̤htyathè̌ tahenuô a nuô̤thò̌nuô̤ǔ lò̌ hò́. Thǐhyethǐca̤ tahenuô akrè̤́ elò̌ hò́.
Thǐrû̌thǐhtè̌ tahenuô a hte-ihtekrè́ lò̌hò́. Tè̤hte-ihtekrè́ yěnuôma a ki khyáluô̌ ná thǐ tè̤thû́ o pǎ rò a ki ekyǎ thǐpháthǐzye phú miû̌kyǎ thǐ nuô pǎ. Thǐ tè̤duzá̤htyathè̌ tahenuô, thǐ beplò́ní̤ pé̤ lò̌hò́ mò̤́nyě dố khyětadûlố yětahe agně hò́.
Ǔ me̤pé̤ thǐlyá̤ rò thǐ dyé ǔ akhwóakè to. Ní̤dǎ mò̌ lahyǎ, èthǐ akhwóakè è́htǒhtyasûhò́ thǐ hò́. Htuô̌rò prè̤kè́plò́dwó pé̤ thǐ buố yětahe tamwǒ̤talè̌ thǐ yěnuô a tuố̤htyahò́ dố tè̤pro̤tè̤prya̤ a Byacè Cò́marya a ohò́, rò a ní̤huô̌ hò́ èthǐ atè̤tamwǒ̤talè̌ yětahe hò́.
Bí thǐ ohtwǒprè̤ dố hekhuyě akhè̌nuô, thǐ lṳ̂me̤mo̤ lốbǎ ní̤dyé htuô̌hò́ thǐ thè́plò ná hekhu atè̤mo̤ tahe hò́. Thǐ me̤bûme̤thú ní̤dyé hò́ thǐné̤ thyáná tè̤phútè̤lye̤ nuôhò́, manárò tè̤phútè̤lye̤ yěnuô ǔ ki me̤thyě èthǐ shyé꤮ tè̤me̤thyě amò̤́nyě nuôtônyě pǎnuô a thè́gně ní̤dyé lahyǎ ané̤to.
Ǔtè̤thû́ oto tadû́rò thǐ cirya me̤thyěkyǎ ǔ, manárò èthǐ me̤tǎ̤tṳ̂̌ ka̤khyěsûbè́ thǐ tôcô꤮ to.
Tè̤khyáthè́dǒ Ná Tè̤kwǐcò́bè̌
Phúnuôrò puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, khyáthè́dǒ tuố̤ lahyǎ dố Byacè hyǎ khyěthyá pǎ tôphuố yěnuô ní꤮. Tane̤myá kuô̌ lahyǎ mò̌ prè̤hyǎelyá̤phú tôprè̤ opò̤́myásû̌ ní̤dyé a tè̤thètè̤phǒ dố angṳdupri̤du yětahenuô. A bè cáhtya khyáthè́plòhtǔ opò̤́ní̤ ké̤cṳ̂ tǎ̤ lú yě dố a me̤dyáhtya pé̤ lǔ tè̤klwǐtè̤lwí yětahe, htuô̌rò a bè opò̤́ tuố̤dố ké̤cṳ̂ tǎ̤no dốkhyě dố a me̤prè̤́me̤mǐ pé̤ lǔ tè̤thètè̤phǒ yětahe.
Thǐ bèbè thǐ tǒ khyáthè́dǒkuô̌ phúnuô. Tarú dyaklò̤ma lahyǎ thǐ tè̤myásû̌ nuô, me̤těhérò Byacè ki hyǎ khyěthyá pǎnuô, amò̤́nyě phûlǎ hò́.
Puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, thyáphú thǐ ki khyábè tǎ tè̤cirya tǎmé̤nuô, tamwǒ̤talè̌ tǎ lǔ tôprè̤ ná tôprè̤ tǎmé̤. Prè̤cirya tè̤ yětôprè̤ hyǎotuố̤phû tatòhò́ dố kadǎhtû̌ hò́.
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, thè́né̤htyabè tuố̤ lahyǎ prè̤pro̤ dố a hébè dố Byacè amwi̤ akǔ nuôtahe ní꤮. Bí thǐ myáhtye sítôbè ná tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ akhè̌nuô, myábû̌kuô̌ èthǐ khyáthè́dǒbè́ htuô̌hò́ tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ nuôtahe ní꤮.
Kayǎ dố a khyáthè́plòhtǔ bè́ nuô, pè̤ hé è ná kayǎ dố a ní̤bè tè̤sò̌ri. Thǐ ní̤huô̌ htuô̌dûhò́ Joba a tè̤khyáthè́dǒ ari-akyǎ hò́ rò dố khyětadû rò Byacè taze-one ná a ki sò̌ri lǔ phútě ari-akyǎ nuô, thǐ thè́gně hò́. Me̤těhérò Byacè a tè̤thè́zò̤klabè yěnuô alốabǎ nyacò́.
Puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, dố tè̤lò̌꤮ plǐ aklè̌nuô, tè̤ dố a lodulố꤮ tôcôma má̤hò́ bí thǐ ò́lya̤ tè̤tôcôcô akhè̌nuô, byǎ tǎ thǐné̤ ná mò́khu, má̤torò hekhu, kimá̤torò dố tè̤ aruô tôcôcô a mèthènyě phúnuô tǎmé̤ ní꤮. Thyáphú thǐ ki siplè́ ná tè̤cirya agněnuô, a ki má̤ rò “amá̤,” hé phúnuô, a ki má̤to hérò “amá̤to,” hé phúnuô prè́ ní꤮.
Dố thǐklè̌ nuô, kayǎ bèpyá̤bèsè̌ o tôprè̤prè̤ è̌? A ki o hérò, a tǒkò kwǐcò́bè̌ tè̤. A thè́krṳ̂̌thè́lò̌ o tôprè̤prè̤ è̌? A ki o hérò, a tǒkò irǒ htuthè́htya Cò́marya.
Dố thǐklè̌ nuô, kayǎswíkayǎsè̌ o tôprè̤prè̤ è̌? A ki o hérò, a tǒkò è́ prè̤zṳ̂́etè̤plò́mṳ muố̤prû̌muố̤prè̤́ dố a htwǒ khuklò́khuklyǎ tahe rò muố̤prû̌muố̤prè̤́ yětahe ki plò̤́ lǔ ná htahtyě dố Byacè amwi̤ akǔ rò èthǐ tǒkò kwǐcò́bè̌ pé̤ dố lǔgně.
Tè̤zṳ̂́tè̤nyá̤ a tè̤kwǐcò́bè̌ yě a ki zasǐmé̤kyǎ kayǎswí yětôprè̤ pǎ. Byacè ki zasǐmé̤ ka̤khyě khyěthyá lǔ pǎ rò a ki me̤thû́ tè̤ hérò Byacè ki plwǒkyǎ khyěthyá lǔ tè̤thû́ pǎ.
Phúnuôrò, ò́lya̤ lahyǎ thǐ tè̤thû́ tahe tôprè̤ ná tôprè̤, rò thyáphú thǐ ki oshyo-opryǎ ka̤khyě agněnuô, kwǐcò́bè̌ pé̤ lǔ tôprè̤ ná tôprè̤ ní꤮. Kayǎcò́kayǎte̤ tôprè̤ a tè̤kwǐcò́bè̌ nuô a o ná a taryěshyosò̌ rò a me̤cwó̤bè́ è́꤮ nyacò́ tè̤tahe cò́.
Prè̤pro̤ Elia ma kayǎ tôprè̤ dố a thyáprè́ phú vǎ ná nè̤ yěnuôprè́. Rò thyáphú ké̤ ki cṳ̂tǎ̤ tǎmé̤ agněnuô, a kwǐcò́bè̌ lò̌thulò̌thè́ akhu-akhyě, ké̤klakyǎ thuô̌na ná lè̌thuô̌thyó cò́.
A kwǐcò́bè̌ khyě tôphuố rò ké̤cṳ̂ tǎ̤ khyěthyá, rò thòmò̤́vèbǒ tahe thèhtyaphǒhtya khyěthyá.
Vǎ puố̤vyá̤ thǐ꤮, dố thǐklè̌nuô kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ a ki cuốpè̤̌kyǎ ná tè̤má̤tè̤cò́ hérò kayǎ dố aruôtôprè̤ ki cuố è́ka̤tǒ khyěthyá lǔ dố klyákǔ hénuô,
thè́né̤htyabè lahyǎ, kayǎ tôprè̤prè̤ dố a cuố è́ka̤tǒ khyěthyá prè̤oraphú dố a krwǒ cuốthû́nò́ klyá yětôprè̤prè̤ nuôma má̤hò́ a me̤lwóhteka̤ kayǎ yětôprè̤ a thè́htwǒprè̤ dố tè̤thyě hò́. Htuô̌to thyáphú Cò́marya ki plwǒkyǎ kayǎ yětôprè̤ atè̤thû́ è́cô agněnuô, a me̤cwó̤ pé̤hò́ lǔ hò́.
Petru Aré̤lố Tôba
Tè̤hébè Ré̤ Dố Nyě
Li Petru aré̤lố yětôba nuôma, a rǎcuố pé̤ Krístuphú dố a cuốo sipryǎ lahyǎ dố Asia Minor ké̤ cíhtǒ nuôtôkyě tahe. Bí liyětôba akǔnuô, Cò́marya kayǎ dố a nwóhtya ní̤dyé tahe, a è́ ní̤dyé lǔ phúnuô. Li yětôba a tè̤taze myásû̌ní̤ ma má̤hò́ a ki dyéhè̌dyére ní̤ prè̤hốli dố a zṳ̂́e Jesǔ rò dố a tè̤zṳ̂́ khukhyě a sítôbè ná tè̤me̤cyě̤me̤cṳ̂, a khyábè tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ thǐtahe. Dố a dyé thè́né̤htya ka̤khyě khyěthyá a prè̤hốli tahe ná Jesǔ Krístu a tè̤thè́krṳ̂̌mila akhu-akhyě a dyéhè̌dyére hò́ èthǐ hò́. Thyáphú èthǐ ki cṳ̌ bè́ phyésûbè́, khyáthè́plòhtǔbè́ kuô̌ lahyǎ tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ dố a hyǎbè èthǐ yětahenuô rò, Jesǔ atè̤thyě, ná a tè̤thyěihtò htwǒprè̤ ka̤khyě, ná a ò́lya̤kyǎ pé̤ ǔ ná a ki hyǎ khyěthyá pǎ ari-akyǎ yětahenuô, a dyé pé̤ hò́ Krístuphú tahe a tè̤myásû̌ hò́. Thyáphú ǔ ki thè́gně ná tè̤zṳ̂́ yěnuôma amá̤ è̌, ma amá̤ to è̌ nuôrò, èthǐ tè̤zṳ̂́ yěnuô, tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ tahe bè me̤myá è. Kayǎ tahenuô, a tǒ khyáthè́plòhtǔ lahyǎ tè̤pyá̤tè̤sè̌ tè̤cyě̤tè̤cṳ̂ tahe, htuô̌to a tǒ zṳ̂́ení̤ lahyǎ ná shyé꤮ Jesǔ Krístu hyǎ khyěthyá pǎnuô, èthǐ ki ní̤bè tè̤me̤ní̤khwókè pǎ.
Prè̤rǎliyě a dyéhè̌dyérení̤ kuô̌dû prè̤hốli thǐ tahe ná a ki ohtwǒprè̤ lahyǎ phú èthǐ ma a htwǒhò́ Krístu akayǎ tahe hò́, phúnuô.
